FORETHICA: "For Ethical Choice" recycled polyester microfleeceDEUS EX MACHINA presents Deus Powdertools Alternative Snowcraft.Influenced by our fondness of deep powdery days in the snowy mountains, DEUS POWDER TOOLS was a notion conjured up by Japan DEUS chapter. With steady snowfall common in the mountainous regions of the country, frosty winters are a part of life for many here. The Snowsurf subculture has been around in Japan for decades and the Japanese have been experimenting with hand-shaped edgeless snow craft for some time now. Deus Powdertools snowboards incorporate those radical tail and nose concepts to innovative technology and material applications for ... easy carve, awesome float, and smooth glide snow craft.At a glance, this collection of odd-shaped boards appears to be created specifically for the fluffy white stuff, but these alternative shapes are designed to carve exceptionally on groomed runs as well as excel in deep powder.What started out 6 years ago together with established surfboard builder Takuya Tappy Yoshikawa, as a design experiment in innovative Snowsurf boards has become an extension of Deus 'culture of Creativity' in Japan.A natural progression from commutes to the snowy peaks came a desire to create a "Metro to Mountain" apparel collection under the same name for these cold winter trips. Being dressed for the cold weather makes smart sense but being smartly dressed for the city is sensible too.

The Dice is your daily driver when  the mercury deems fit - box fit, snug construction resulting in timeless, understated style.

Chances are there’s only room for one Dub Bass-esque shirt in your wardrobe (unless you’re that guy), so let us make the case for this bold little number. It’s bright, bordering on garish, but surprisingly easy to pair. The fit’s relaxed so it works as well over a pair of slacks as it does a pair of trunks, and it’s made from 100% Cotton sheeting.

When most people think ‘knitted’ they conjure some fuzzed out stink-fest, but the A-Frame  is a knit without the hang ups. Perfect for those fresh mornings and fast-cooling evenings  as the seasons transition in and out of winter. It’s a regular fit, raglan sleeve knit made  from a recycled wool/nylon blend that feels like heaven against salty skin.
